	<p>Whether you&rsquo;re competing in the Pokemon GO Championship Series or studying for your next <a href="https://silph.gg/" target="_blank">Silph Arena</a> cup, Pokemon GO tournament play brings a wide array of strategies and decisions to the table. This article covers the rules of &ldquo;show 6, pick 3&rdquo; tournament play, team building strategies, and scenarios to think about as your tournament unfolds. In addition, you&rsquo;ll find advice from veteran tournament players to help you on our journey to be the very best. Huge thanks for their contributions!</p>
